description:
The image is a screenshot of a mobile device display, likely an event invitation or schedule related to a conference or meeting. The top of the screen shows the time "22:04," the date "31," and a battery indicator showing 29% charge.

The first section of the event description encourages attendees to visit the MGM lobby, specifically to see the Lion and the Las Vegas sign, take pictures, and return. A button labeled "RSVP NOW" is visible, suggesting attendees confirm their participation.

The second section details a "Playable Ads Generation 1:1 Live Demo" scheduled from 9:00 AM to 4:00 PM, with the user's local time being 6:00 - 13:00. The description highlights the AI-powered process that uses game video to create interactive and performance-ready playable ads. Key features include the ability to choose vertical or horizontal formats, plug in gameplay footage without design needs, generate interactive scenes quickly, and create launch-ready creatives in under 10 minutes. A button labeled "BOOK YOUR DEMO" is provided.

Below, it's noted that the event is "Sponsored by: Appier."

A final section indicates a session from 12:00 PM to 1:00 PM in Meeting Room 256, and it includes a prompt to "Ask a question about MAU."

In the lower part of the screen, there is a floating button with a cookie icon, and a chat bubble icon. The navigation bar for the mobile device is also visible.
